Predict method for gamem fits

Source: R/gamem.R
predict.gamem.Rd

Obtains predictions from an object fitted with gamem.

# S3 method for gamem
predict(object, ...)

Arguments

object

An object of class gamem
...

Currently not used

Value

A tibble with the predicted values for each variable in the model

Examples

# \donttest{
library(metan)
model <- gamem(data_g,
              gen = GEN,
              rep = REP,
              resp = everything())
#> Model:  Y ~ REP + (1 | GEN)
